description: After his victory over Luke Riley, Leo Forte is back and he's more confident than ever. Alessio Romero approached Van at the gym asking for a shot at NK. Well, here is his chance. Both burly guys are going at it with their buttholes at stake. Also new to NK is Scott Tanner, the new ref. Scott will be adding some twists to NK in the near future. Please stay tuned.
title: Leo Forte vs Alessio Romero
